OL,3,CCumbria police welcome jail time for
OL,4,Cman who encouraged violence against
OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FCumbria Police has welcomed a jail
OL,8,Fsentence for a man from Carlisle who
OL,9,Fencouraged violence against officers
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,FStuart Burns, 41, of Briar Bank,
OL,13,FCarlisle, has been found guilty of two
OL,14,Foffences under Section 127 of the
OL,15,FCommunications Act, appearing at North
OL,16,FCumbria Magistrates Court on 29 August
OL,17,F2024.
