OL,3,CCumbria police welcome jail time for
OL,4,Cman who encouraged violence against
OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FPosting on social media between 2
OL,8,FAugust and 6 August 2024, the court
OL,9,Fheard how Burns encouraged people to
OL,10,Fact violently towards the police,
OL,11,Fincluding the destruction of police
OL,12,Fvehicles and equipment relating to
OL,13,Fpotential planned disorder.
OL,15,FBurns was sentenced to 14 weeks in
OL,16,Fprison.
OL,18,FChief Superintendent Carl Patrick said
OL,19,F"officers should not come to work with
OL,20,Fthe fear of being assaulted".
