OL,3,CCumbria police welcome jail time for
OL,4,Cman who encouraged violence against
OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FHe said: "This sentence makes clear
OL,8,Fthose inciting violence online will
OL,9,Fface the consequences. Burns
OL,10,Fencouraged people to target the police.
OL,12,F"Our officers should not come to work
OL,13,Fwith the fear of being assaulted and
OL,14,Fthe majority of the public understand
OL,15,Fthis and show respect to the police as
OL,16,Fthey go about their important work to
OL,17,Fkeep people safe.
